```

Instead of this:
```cs
// some notes, etc. etc. etc. etc. etc. etc. etc. etc. etc. etc.

// some other notes  etc. etc. etc. etc. etc. etc. etc. etc. etc.
```

In all other collapsings, the code blocks are collapsed separately. But if it is two comments blocks then they are merged.

I think if they are separated then they are not related and so must be collapsed separately. It is very frustrating that we have many documentations in our code, but they are always collapsed into one mega collapse... hard to find what we are looking for.

Thank you.

